OL,3,C'Motherhood penalty' fuels pension
OL,4,Cgender gap crisis
OL,6,FHowever, women still earn 9% less than
OL,7,Fmen within the Civil Service, which
OL,8,Fcan have a knock-on impact for those
OL,9,Fpaying into private pensions,
OL,10,Fespecially if they have children.
OL,12,FDr Daniella Jenkins from the UK's
OL,13,FWomen's Budget Group raised her
OL,14,Fconcerns about women in pension
OL,15,Fpoverty in the House of Commons and
OL,16,Fhas been at the forefront of new
OL,17,Freforms in the UK.
